column2: SELECT u.up_name as [name], # + cast (x.objId as varchar (#) ) + #+ cast (x.objId as varchar (#) ) + # as objID, p.ra, p.dec, dbo.fPhotoTypeN (p.type) as type, p.cmodelMag_u, p.cmodelMagErr_u, p.cmodelMag_g, p.cmodelMagErr_g, p.cmodelMag_r, p.cmodelMagErr_r, p.cmodelMag_i, p.cmodelMagErr_i, p.cmodelMag_z, p.cmodelMagErr_z FROM #upload u JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = x.objID ORDER BY x.up_id
